<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tristan Imkamp — Digital CV</title>
    <meta
            name="description"
            content="Digitaler Lebenslauf und Portfolio von Tristan Imkamp."
    />
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0a0f1b;
            --bg-soft: #111827;
            --card: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.72);
            --text: #e5edf5;
            --muted: #94a3b8;
            --accent: #64ffda;
            --border: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18);
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
            --max: 1160px;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            background:
                    radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.08), transparent 24%),
                    radial-gradient(circle at left center, rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.05), transparent 20%),
                    var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a {
            color: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            display: block;
        }

        .page {
            max-width: var(--max);
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        .layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
            gap: 56px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .sidebar {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 56px 0 40px;
        }

        .brand small,
        .eyebrow {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .brand h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
            line-height: 1;
            margin: 10px 0 14px;
        }

        .brand p {
            color: var(--muted);
            max-width: 18rem;
        }

        .nav {
            margin-top: 42px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .nav a {
            color: var(--muted);
            transition: 0.2s ease;
            width: fit-content;
        }

        .nav a:hover,
        .nav a.active {
            color: var(--text);
            transform: translateX(6px);
        }

        .socials {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .socials a:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        main {
            padding: 56px 0 96px;
        }

        section {
            padding: 42px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        section:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 82vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-inner {
            max-width: 760px;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 5rem);
            line-height: 0.98;
            margin: 12px 0 22px;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            max-width: 640px;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            margin-top: 28px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn {
            border: 1px solid var(--accent);
            color: var(--accent);
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            transition: 0.2s ease;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.08);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn.secondary {
            border-color: var(--border);
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin: 10px 0 20px;
        }

        .about-text {
            max-width: 760px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .about-text p + p {
            margin-top: 14px;
        }

        .timeline {
            display: grid;
            gap: 18px;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 22px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: var(--card);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: 0.2s ease;
        }

        .timeline-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.35);
        }

        .timeline-year {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .timeline-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .timeline-content .company {
            color: var(--text);
            opacity: 0.88;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .timeline-content p {
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .tags {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }

        .tag {
            border: 1px solid rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.18);
            background: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.06);
            color: var(--accent);
            padding: 6px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.84rem;
        }

        .projects {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
            margin-top: 18px;
        }

        .project {
            padding: 22px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: var(--card);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: 0.2s ease;
        }

        .project:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.35);
        }

        .project h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .project p {
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .project-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 14px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .project-links a {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .skills-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
            margin-top: 18px;
        }

        .skill-card {
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: var(--card);
        }

        .skill-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .skill-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            color: var(--muted);
            display: grid;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .contact-card {
            padding: 26px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: var(--card);
            max-width: 720px;
        }

        .contact-card p {
            color: var(--muted);
            margin: 10px 0 18px;
        }

        .footer {
            padding-top: 22px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.92rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 960px) {
            .layout {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 0;
            }

            .sidebar {
                position: relative;
                height: auto;
                padding-bottom: 12px;
            }

            .nav {
                flex-direction: row;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }

            .hero {
                min-height: auto;
                padding-top: 22px;
            }

            .projects,
            .skills-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .timeline-item {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .page {
                padding: 0 18px;
            }

            main {
                padding-top: 12px;
            }

            .hero h2 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
    <div class="layout">
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <div>
                <div class="brand">
                    <small>Digital CV</small>
                    <h1>Tristan Imkamp</h1>
                    <p>
                        Frontend-orientierter Entwickler mit Fokus auf saubere Interfaces,
                        klare Struktur und moderne Web-Erlebnisse.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <nav class="nav">
                    <a href="#about">About</a>
                    <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
                    <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
                    <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
                    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
                </nav>
            </div>

            <div class="socials">
                <a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="mailto:mail@example.com">Mail</a>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main>
            <section class="hero">
                <div class="hero-inner">
                    <div class="eyebrow">Hallo — ich bin Tristan</div>
                    <h2>
                        Ich entwickle klare, moderne und funktionale Weboberflächen.
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Diese Seite ist mein digitaler Lebenslauf: Erfahrung, ausgewählte
                        Projekte, technische Schwerpunkte und ein direkter Weg, mich zu
                        kontaktieren.
                    </p>

                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a class="btn" href="#projects">Projekte ansehen</a>
                        <a class="btn secondary" href="/cv.pdf">CV als PDF</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="about">
                <div class="eyebrow">About</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Kurzprofil</h2>
                <div class="about-text">
                    <p>
                        Ich mag Interfaces, die schnell sind, logisch aufgebaut wirken und
                        sich gut anfühlen. Mich interessieren besonders Frontend-Architektur,
                        visuelle Qualität und die Verbindung aus Design und Umsetzung.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Statt möglichst viel zu zeigen, will ich hier die Dinge zeigen, die
                        wirklich relevant sind: Erfahrung, Arbeitsweise, Projekte und Stack.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="experience">
                <div class="eyebrow">Experience</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Beruflicher Werdegang</h2>

                <div class="timeline">
                    <article class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2024 — heute</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Frontend Developer</h3>
                            <div class="company">Firma / Projektname</div>
                            <p>
                                Entwicklung und Pflege moderner Webinterfaces mit Fokus auf
                                Performance, UI-Konsistenz und sauberer Komponentenstruktur.
                            </p>
                            <div class="tags">
                                <span class="tag">TypeScript</span>
                                <span class="tag">React</span>
                                <span class="tag">Next.js</span>
                                <span class="tag">UI Systems</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2022 — 2024</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Web Developer</h3>
                            <div class="company">Firma / Projektname</div>
                            <p>
                                Umsetzung responsiver Websites und Features, enge Zusammenarbeit
                                mit Design und iterative Verbesserung bestehender Produkte.
                            </p>
                            <div class="tags">
                                <span class="tag">JavaScript</span>
                                <span class="tag">CSS</span>
                                <span class="tag">Accessibility</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="projects">
                <div class="eyebrow">Selected Work</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Ausgewählte Projekte</h2>

                <div class="projects">
                    <article class="project">
                        <h3>Projekt Eins</h3>
                        <p>
                            Kurze Beschreibung: Problem, Lösung und was dein Beitrag war.
                            Maximal 3–4 Zeilen.
                        </p>
                        <div class="tags">
                            <span class="tag">React</span>
                            <span class="tag">TypeScript</span>
                            <span class="tag">API</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="project-links">
                            <a href="#">Live</a>
                            <a href="#">Code</a>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="project">
                        <h3>Projekt Zwei</h3>
                        <p>
                            Ein zweites Projekt mit klarem Nutzen und kurzem Fokus auf deinen
                            Impact statt nur auf Technologie.
                        </p>
                        <div class="tags">
                            <span class="tag">Next.js</span>
                            <span class="tag">UI</span>
                            <span class="tag">Performance</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="project-links">
                            <a href="#">Live</a>
                            <a href="#">Code</a>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="project">
                        <h3>Projekt Drei</h3>
                        <p>
                            Zeige hier etwas, das dich unterscheidet: Tooling, visuelles
                            Feingefühl oder besondere technische Lösung.
                        </p>
                        <div class="tags">
                            <span class="tag">Design System</span>
                            <span class="tag">Frontend</span>
                            <span class="tag">UX</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="project-links">
                            <a href="#">Live</a>
                            <a href="#">Code</a>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <article class="project">
                        <h3>Playground</h3>
                        <p>
                            Dein Playground kann bleiben — aber als bewusste Unterkategorie
                            für kleine Experimente oder visuelle Ideen.
                        </p>
                        <div class="tags">
                            <span class="tag">Creative Coding</span>
                            <span class="tag">Experiments</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="project-links">
                            <a href="#">Mehr</a>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="skills">
                <div class="eyebrow">Stack</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Technische Schwerpunkte</h2>

                <div class="skills-grid">
                    <div class="skill-card">
                        <h3>Frontend</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>HTML / CSS / JavaScript</li>
                            <li>TypeScript</li>
                            <li>React / Next.js</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="skill-card">
                        <h3>UI & Qualität</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Responsive Design</li>
                            <li>Accessibility</li>
                            <li>Performance</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="skill-card">
                        <h3>Workflow</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Git / GitHub</li>
                            <li>Component Thinking</li>
                            <li>Saubere Übergabe von Design zu Code</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="contact">
                <div class="eyebrow">Contact</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Lass uns sprechen</h2>

                <div class="contact-card">
                    <p>
                        Ob Job, Freelance-Projekt oder einfach Austausch über Frontend,
                        Design und Webentwicklung — schreib mir gern.
                    </p>
                    <a class="btn" href="mailto:mail@example.com">E-Mail schreiben</a>
                </div>

                <div class="footer">
                    Design & Code by Tristan Imkamp
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
